               stealing, on the <rs id="t18280110-23-cd114" type="crimeDate">21st of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280110-23-off113 t18280110-23-cd114"></join>, 1 pair of shoes, value 2s. 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18280110-23-victim244" type="victimName">
                  Alexander 
                  Wilson
               <interp inst="t18280110-23-victim244" type="surname" value="Wilson"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280110-23-victim244" type="given" value="Alexander"></interp>
